&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Medical Receptionist at Werrington Village Surgery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2 receptionist  x 20 hours per week (each) over 4 days as per rota&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to retirement we have an opportunity for two part time medical receptionists to join our very busy team. You will have great customer care skills and ideally call centre experience. The role will be varied and flexibility is a must ! You will provide a professional, approachable first point of contact for patients, medical professionals and the public contacting the practice by telephone and in person. You will be directing patients to the most appropriate health service / clinician.   &lt;/p&gt;
